hite billionaires make those decisions for everyone? Even if you approve of their decisions this time, what seeds do we sew when we outsource those decisions to them? Will \u201Cexperts\u201D always have the experience of marginalized people in mind? Have they in the past?"), mdx("p", null, "A part of me feels these edge cases where we want to make an exception and throw sovereignty away, are actually the most important to pay extra attention to, to bring about deeper change, which is why I write this. "), mdx("p", null, "With many questions, "), mdx("p", null, "M"));
